{"id":1093661,"date":[{"year":1997,"month":5,"day":31}],"page":"9","source":"","region":"","masthead":"文汇特刊","special_issue":"星星岛","column":"小小作家","genre":"","count":"129","ytitle":"","mtitle":"春天是什么?","ftitle":"","authors":["郑好"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天是什么?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳公公说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“春天是暖洋洋的阳光照遍大地!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨娃娃说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“春天是给种子浇水!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青蛙说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“春天是从冬眠的泥洞里钻出来!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“春天是一座永不停息的大时钟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它告诉我们——一年之计在于春。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闸北区实验小学三(5)班　郑好"}]}